  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Gardener\" title=\"Garth Gardener\">Garth Gardener</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Garth\" title=\"Garth\">Garth</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/50px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/75px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/100px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Garth V Gardener<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Hammer of the Dornish</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/50px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/75px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/100px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nGarth of House Gardener, the Fifth of His Name</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nHammer of the Dornish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Garth V Gardener</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a>. He was dubbed <b>Hammer of the Dornish</b> for his legendary conflicts with <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf772_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf772-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_scenes\">Behind the scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_V_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Garth V may be inspired by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_I_of_England\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Edward I of England\">Edward I of England</a>, who was known as the Hammer of the Scots.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_V_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf772-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf772_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Seven Kingdoms&#58; The Reach&#32;(The Gardener Kings).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403165546\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.254 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 550/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11084/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7616/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 433/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 415/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.62 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  243.878      1 -total\n 85.90%  209.486      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 85.02%  207.341      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.32%   30.046     14 Template:Infobox_value\n 11.62%   28.349      1 Template:See_homonyms\n  4.29%   10.456      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.81%    4.422      1 T